metadata.name: Light Mode
metadata.description: This NFT merges the digital and physical realms by capturing the essence of a user's online presence in the form of a one-of-a-kind, verifiable, and transferable digital asset. The color scheme of a user's profile, as well as the geometric shape of the profile, serve as visual representations of the individual's personal style and online persona, making this NFT a symbol of self-expression and individuality in the digital space
